data.description: Welcome to the heart of San Tan Valley bordering Queen Creek. This charming 3 bed 2.5 bath 2 car garage features an open concept floor plan with new new vinyl plank flooring and baseboards on first level. No wasted space upstairs and plenty of storage. Existing water softness and RO system plumbed for your convenience. Refrigerator, washer/dryer, and above ground spa included. Newer AC installed in 2020, partial re-roof 2022. Don't miss out on this one and make this your home today!
